Comment: 1,0:00:11.12,0:00:13.55,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,夢想受到束縛
Comment: 1,0:00:14.08,0:00:16.26,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,沉重命運的意志
Comment: 1,0:00:16.58,0:00:19.68,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,如同被壓迫直至覆滅
Comment: 1,0:00:21.61,0:00:24.05,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,前方已無處逃避
Comment: 1,0:00:24.35,0:00:26.64,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,唯有掙扎著前行
Comment: 1,0:00:27.00,0:00:30.82,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是我永遠不會放棄
Comment: 1,0:00:30.87,0:00:36.79,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,瓦礫之中埋藏的
Comment: 1,0:00:36.93,0:00:41.85,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,希望的碎片
Comment: 1,0:00:42.63,0:00:47.41,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,用這雙手 將它們找尋
Comment: 1,0:00:47.50,0:00:52.92,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,只為改變這世間
Comment: 1,0:00:55.61,0:00:58.28,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,Fighting Gold
Comment: 1,0:00:58.34,0:01:08.05,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,唯有相信自己的內心之人 終有一天方能閃耀
Comment: 1,0:01:08.69,0:01:16.94,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,燃燒全部生命 即便是神亦無畏懼 戰鬥永不停息
Comment: 1,0:01:17.18,0:01:21.66,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,不屈的魂靈
Comment: 1,0:01:24.40,0:01:27.08,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,Fighting Gold
